description:
https://www.playstation.com/accessories/playstation-portal-remote-player/

Let play run wild and free with the PlayStation Portal™ remote player. 

With a handheld gateway to your PS5® console*, amazing play is no longer confined to the same four walls. 
Continue enjoying your favourite PS5 games as you move throughout your house, garden and beyond.

Feel the power of PlayStation® in the palm of your hand with support for immersive DualSense® controller features**. And take in silky-smooth gameplay at up to 60fps through the remote player's expansive 8" 1080p resolution display***.

With the PlayStation Portal remote player, you can transform when, where and how you play.

*PlayStation Portal remote player can stream compatible games installed on your PS5 console. PlayStation Portal remote player requires broadband internet Wi-Fi with at least 5Mbps for use. For a better play experience, a connection of at least 15Mbps is recommended. The quality and connectivity of your play experie
title: Play Finds a Way with PlayStation Portal | PS5

author: PlayStation
description:
Rugby 25 is available now on PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4!

Step out of the locker room and get ready to take the field in some of the world’s biggest rugby stadiums in Rugby 25. 

With over 140 international teams, 150 clubs from 11 major competitions, including the URC, English Premiership, French Top 14, MLR, Super Rugby, and, for the first time in a rugby game, a substantial number of the best women’s rugby teams, Rugby 25 offers the most comprehensive content ever seen.

With innovative gameplay and realistic player behaviour, Rugby 25 is the most authentic rugby video game to date, where tactical decisions and physical effort are the keys to victory!

Are you ready for action?

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #rugby25
title: Rugby 25 - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games

description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10007412/

Ready to take on a new challenge in Taxi Life with the new Delivery Driver DLC? 

Many of you have already mastered Taxi Life by completing it 100%, but now it's time for something fresh! The brand-new DLC introduces the thrilling ""Delivery Driver"" game mode, where you’ll need to deliver packages safely and in top condition while navigating the vibrant streets of Barcelona.

But that’s not all, meet your new ride, the Victoris pick-up truck, designed to handle all your delivery missions with style and efficiency. Whether you're a seasoned player or just starting your journey, this DLC has something for everyone.

Start your engines and get ready to experience Taxi Life like never before!

Our Delivery Driver DLC is available on PlayStation®5.

#ps5 #ps5games #taxilifeacitydrivingsimulator
title: Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator - Delivery Driver DLC Trailer | PS5 Games
